---

### Summary

Issue #291 is the onboarding epic. Sub-issues #271, #272, #273 are all closed and PR #619 implemented the bulk of the work. One spec requirement from #273 was missed: the `My Profile` section in SettingsPanel shows `"Profile not available."` for new users, but `docs/UX_STRATEGY.md` requires it to say `"As we talk, I'll learn how you like to work. You can always edit what I've picked up."` — a meaningful onboarding message instead of an error-like fallback.

